Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.12,0:22:57.35,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(491,390)\fad(350,0)}{\3c&H0000FF&}{\bord2}待續…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【下回預告】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.69,0:22:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.88,0:23:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是贏了小亮的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.21,0:23:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先放三子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.49,0:23:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是小亮的實力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.10,0:23:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我? 職業棋手?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.29,0:23:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事情我從來都沒想過
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.46,0:23:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為一個棋手 怎麼能說出那麼低俗的話!

